body:
So generally, i can handle all types of toxicity, but the one that gets me is when, they just say bitchy passive aggressive things, that don&#039;t really warrant a mute, but they keep going and going and going, (they are usually performing horribly and in this case are actually the reason we lost)

The team, just politely ignores this person then BAM, they drop the passive aggressive, start hardcore flaming, blaming everyone else.
Then someone snaps (was me this time) and just goes &quot;shut up and fucking play dude. holy&quot;

THEN BAM! &quot;/all chat report amumu for flaming me. been talking shit all game. im trying my hardest&quot;

it actually tilts me to the moon. 
i want to pick up my computer, and throw it into an active volcano.
